{"title":"利用gitee搭建免费图床","uid":"b3409e69842024b2b1c08152bfc1aaf4","slug":"利用gitee搭建免费图床","date":"2021-11-10T13:18:44.000Z","updated":"2021-12-15T12:43:12.115Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/利用gitee搭建免费图床.json","keywords":null,"cover":"https://gitee.com/chenxz21/pic/raw/master/images/202112152037042.jpg","content":"<hr>\n<span id=\"more\"></span>\n\n\n\n<center>如果没有注册gitee请访问此网站进行注册(https://gitee.com/)</center>\n\n<img src=\"https://gitee.com/chenxz21/pic/raw/master/images/202111102124519.png\" alt=\"O_JO}BEFE{2A9PPPPSQF{T7\" style=\"zoom: 50%;\" />\n\n<center>如果注册过了，直接登录即可</center>\n\n<center>登录之后点击右上角头像左边的加号，点击新建仓库</center>\n\n<img src=\"https://gitee.com/chenxz21/pic/raw/master/images/202111102129808.png\" alt=\"222\" style=\"zoom: 50%;\" />\n\n<center>填写仓库名和路径，仓库设置为开源，点击创建</center>\n\n<img src=\"https://gitee.com/chenxz21/pic/raw/master/images/202111102136737.png\" alt=\"3333\" style=\"zoom: 50%;\" />\n\n<center>创建成功如下图，点击图中的初始化readme文件，初始化仓库</center>\n\n<img src=\"https://gitee.com/chenxz21/pic/raw/master/images/202111102138688.png\" alt=\"image-20211110213840342\" style=\"zoom: 50%;\" />\n\n<center>然后点击服务，点击gitee pages</center>\n\n<center>(一个账号只能开启一个giteepages服务，所以下图是我开giteepages服务的仓库)</center>\n\n<img src=\"https://gitee.com/chenxz21/pic/raw/master/images/202111102143999.png\" alt=\"555\" style=\"zoom: 50%;\" />\n\n<center>因为gitee在国内，所以依照法律规定需要进行实名认证，以防有人发布不良信息</center>\n\n<center>认证很快，如果不想认证，可以使用国外的github搭建，下图是我认证后的页面</center>\n\n<img src=\"https://gitee.com/chenxz21/pic/raw/master/images/202111102148307.png\" alt=\"6666\" style=\"zoom: 50%;\" />\n\n<center>认证成功之后，上图中应该是有开启按钮，点击开启功能之后，即可通过图中的域名访问你上传到仓库中的图片</center>\n\n<center>如我的gitee pages服务域名为 http://chenxz21.gitee.io/pic</center>\n\n<center>我要访问下图中的根目录的文件README.md，访问 http://chenxz21.gitee.io/pic/README.md即可</center>\n\n<img src=\"https://gitee.com/chenxz21/pic/raw/master/images/202111102201212.png\" alt=\"777\" style=\"zoom: 50%;\" />\n\n<center>如要访问根目录的文件夹中的文件，访问http://chenxz21.gitee.io/pic/images/1.jpg即可</center>\n\n<center>如要上传文件的话，可参考下图</center>\n\n<img src=\"https://gitee.com/chenxz21/pic/raw/master/images/202111102205062.png\" alt=\"888\" style=\"zoom: 50%;\" />\n\n<center>教程到此结束</center>\n\n<hr>\n<center>如果不想要作图床使用的话，还可以上传静态html，搭建个人网站使用，本网站就是利用github搭建而来的，如果你不想用gitee分配的域名，请看本站上一篇文章(本站的域名就是由此而来)，有疑问的小伙伴可以在下方评论区评论。</center>\n\n\n\n\n\n<hr>\n","text":" 如果没有注册gitee请访问此网站进行注册(https://gitee.com/) 如果注册过了，直接登录即可 登录之后点击右上角头像左边的加号，点击新建仓库 填写仓库名和路径，仓库设置为开源，点击创建 创建成功如下图，点击图中的初始化readme文件，初始化仓库 然后点击服务...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":686,"symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[],"tags":[{"name":"技术教程","slug":"技术教程","count":1,"path":"api/tags/技术教程.json"}],"toc":"","author":{"name":"Chenxz","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"/images/avatar.jpg","link":"/","description":"","socials":{"github":"https://github.com/chenxz21","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"","zhihu":"","csdn":"","juejin":"","customs":{}}},"mapped":true,"prev_post":{"title":"阿里技术书籍分享","uid":"49d2cff518dabf3abf4b10a63c7e5e30","slug":"阿里技术书籍","date":"2021-11-15T05:46:52.000Z","updated":"2021-12-15T12:42:32.867Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/阿里技术书籍.json","keywords":null,"cover":"https://gitee.com/chenxz21/pic/raw/master/images/202112152036376.jpg","text":" 真的干货满满，学到就是赚到！！！ 资源获取: 阿里云盘分享链接 「阿里技术书籍」链接：https://www.aliyundrive.com/s/kLya75csJc3 ","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":106,"symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[],"tags":[{"name":"技术书籍","slug":"技术书籍","count":2,"path":"api/tags/技术书籍.json"}],"author":{"name":"Chenxz","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"/images/avatar.jpg","link":"/","description":"","socials":{"github":"https://github.com/chenxz21","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"","zhihu":"","csdn":"","juejin":"","customs":{}}}},"next_post":{}}